 @{b}The future
 ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{ub}

 Below is a list of planned features for later releases.  Some will be
 implemented, others will go down in history as a nice idea.

 · Lots of changes are already made for Thor 2.5

 · Make trigger configuration more intuitive
   Delete user  ->  Add users (& maybe check CfgThor setting)

 · Make a wizard mode for CfgSortMail

 · Finish BounceMail.br (external script for automatic message forwarding)

 · Allow configuration of Local2Email, possibly through CfgSortMail
   Let it add addresses to Bcc: or Cc: instead of to address field
   Possibly a setting to read to-addresses from an ASCII file

 · Make it possible to pick up header criteria in CfgSortMail

 · Whatever else comes up.  I'm open for suggestions

@ENDNODE
